/*Intuition :-
    Ekhane proshner moddhe bola hoise je sadi ekta cone icecream toiri korte gele
    2 scope icecream er proyojon hoy . Ekhon duita icecream different bole count
    kora hobe jokhon duita icecream er moddhe thaka duita flavour er moddhe atleast
    ekta different hobe . 

    Jemon chocolate , vanila , butterscotch , strawberry , coffee , pistachew , mango eigula
    diye dui rokom vabe banate parbe ,
    1) Duita scope e ekta same flavour er nibe . chocolate + chocolate .
    2) Duita scope duita vinno flavour er nibe . strawberry + butterscotch.

    Ekhon jodi n songkhok vinno vinno flavour thake tobe oi khan thek duita kore flavour
    niye vinno rokom ice cream bananu jabe nCr(n,2) ti . 
    Tar mane (n * (n-1) / 2) dhoroner vinno flavour er ice cream toiri kora jabe .

    Ekhon amader kache proshne chaise je exactly n ta different type of iceCream toiri
    korte hobe . Ei jonne amra jotobeshi shomvob vinno flavour add kore number kom rakhar
    try korbo . Ekhon jodi dekhi vinno flavour add korar karone number of different ice-
    cream amader required exact number ke cross kore jacche tokhon amader kache thaka 
    flavour notun kore add korte thakbo . Ekhetre ekta notun flavour kebol ekta distinct
    iceCream dite parbe . Jemon 1,1 --- 2,2 --- 3,3 .

    Mone kori 9 ta toiri korte hobe tahole amader approach hobe 

    1,2 -- 2,3 -- 3,4 -- 1,3 -- 1,4 -- 2,4 -- 1,1 -- 2,2 -- 3,3 . Ekhane 5 ta flavour
    use korle amra required target cross kore jabo . Tai 4 ta e add korte hobe . Erpore
    existed flavour er notun scope add korte hobe .

*/

void giveMeMyGloryBack() {
    ll n ; cin >> n ; ll ans = -1 ;
    ll low = 1 ; ll high = 2e9 ;
    while(low<=high){
        ll mid = low + (high-low)/2 ;
        if(mid*(mid-1) <= n*2){
            ans = mid ; low = mid+1 ;
        }else{
            high = mid-1 ;
        }
    }
    cout << ans+(n-(ans*(ans-1)/2)) << endl ;
}
